These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, pop
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, spy
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: may, april
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
2. the fan of pop is in an even position##4
3. the person watching spy movies is the fan of disco##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Music-Genre      | disco  | pop   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | crime   |
| Birthday         | april | may |
| Transport     | jet-ski | taxi    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: avocado, cabbage
City: boston, paris
2 different pets are kept: dog, rat
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: begonia, rose
1. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to boston is the person who growsrose##1
3. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | avocado     | cabbage |
| City   | paris | boston  |
| Pet           | rat         | dog     |
| Flower     | begonia   | rose    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: rock-climbing, hiking
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, entrepreneur
2 different pets are kept: frog, lizard
City: prague, liverpool
1. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
2. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Hobby    | hiking     | rock-climbing |
| Job         | entrepreneur | accountant    |
| Pet         | frog         | lizard        |
| City   | prague         | liverpool    |

