The people's birthday is in 2 different months: january, october
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, salsa
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, soccer
1. the person who's sport is soccer is in an even position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left or far right##3
3. the electrician is the person who's birthday is in january##1
4. the fan of ambient is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Job           | electrician | coach    |
| Birthday   | january       | october |
| Music-Genre           | ambient         | salsa    |
| Sport         | climbing    | soccer   |

