The people prefer 2 different types of sport: water-polo, swimming
There are 2 different nationalities: egyptian, pakistani
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, tram
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the pakistani##1
2. the egyptian is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
3. the person driving the roller is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate | water    |
| Sport         | swimming        | water-polo |
| Nationality         | egyptian          | pakistani     |
| Transport   | roller        | tram     |

 